{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience '<strong>The Descent</strong>,' a first-person psychological horror walking sim, set in the coal mining town of Rockwell Mine. Immerse yourself in the grueling atmosphere of a miners environment and their unsettling encounters deep within the treacherous mines. Assume the role of an investigator who returns to this hometown after journalism school to unveil its mysteries. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Genre: Walking Simulator </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore room-to-room, observing evolving events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the challenges faced by miners. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the untold story of the mine. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play Time:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Approximately 2 hours [ Main Story ] + 1 Hour [ Collectibles + Ghost Capture ] </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710320/extras/G1.gif?t=1736239411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rockwell Mine has been plagued by numerous accidents, disappearances, and unexplained deaths, leaving authorities baffled. Despite countless investigations, the truth remains elusive, leading to the closure of the mine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710320/extras/G3.gif?t=1736239411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a player, you must navigate the perilous mine, document your investigation with a camera, solve the mysteries behind the disappearances, and overcome obstacles while evading the dangers lurking within. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710320/extras/G2.gif?t=1736239411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710320/extras/G8.gif?t=1736239411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710320/extras/G6.gif?t=1736239411\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WARNING:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Epileptic seizures associated with increased sensitivity to light are Possible. Some people may experience seizures when exposed to flashes of light and flashing images that appear in a video</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Rock Well Mine ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/8c689354cd79b1361243a726a59221032f67cd49.jpg"},{"name":"Mine Inquiry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/f8ecb7462579f5cb2153806455d84b3d293432d3.jpg"},{"name":"Deep Exploration","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/83f35e5f9232656be6dfd76f0b659b23aab9eebe.jpg"},{"name":"Into The Abyss","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/b5076437daa68f9a975440f700f6e8f89110ffcc.jpg"},{"name":"Unconscious Encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/39a01982358b23704efc781cfd000b4076fdb149.jpg"},{"name":"Notes Connoisseur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/8751dd58e829c10939c001d71095888328a8ef37.jpg"},{"name":"Memories Unearthed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/e2b301261adfd650305773a1b9b98b529aeb76fa.jpg"},{"name":"Keen Investigator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/ba6fb2f791d483d9e2717e651e62c8c615e750ce.jpg"},{"name":"Note Observer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710320/c450aee2935d7f61da664cc67ed9059a077f06fb.j